        an all-in-one search engine to find your favorite songs on the three services.</p>
      <p class="black-text">This is an application written in Sails.js for a course at the University of Nebraska Omaha, ISQA-4380.
        The goal of the project is to take advantage of at least four different APIs.</p>
      <p class="black-text">We chose to take advantage of the APIs supplied by SoundCloud and YouTube for the music itself,
        and use MusixMatch and OpenAura to provide lyrics for the songs searched for an the artist bios.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

